message.body: Did you have a new years dinner tonight?
No, I didn't. My day was off. So tired but at least it was nice out :) we were going to go to the temple but ended up not going. How did you celebrate?
Just had dinner at my aunts. Big party Friday
Of course. Your family are such party animals hahah!
It was nice out today! Did you get to enjoy the weather?
Not really. Long work day today.
How's it going with the ballroom?
Good. Work started this Tuesday. Moving along quick.
Nice! I want to see pictures when it's done! Especially the chandelier :))) I want to see the one you picked!
